<section class="section1">
	<h2 class="section1-heading">What is vCruit?</h2>
	<p class="section1-tagline">vCruit is a web-based application that enables recruiters to quickly and easily utilize the power of online video in their outbound communications.</p>
  <p class="section1-tagline">It works like this:</p>
  <div class="section1-block">
    <h2 class="section1-numbering">1</h2>
    <p class="lead">Upload a video that showcases your message to the vCruit application.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section1-block">
    <h2 class="section1-numbering">2</h2>
    <p class="lead">Display the video on a landing page designed and branded just for you.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section1-block">
    <h2 class="section1-numbering">3</h2>
    <p class="lead">Embed the video into your emails, InMails, and social media posts.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section1-block">
    <h2 class="section1-numbering">4</h2>
    <p class="lead">Track analytics to see who watches the video and for how long.</p>
  </div>
</section>

